*Adopting Terror *- A husband and wife learn that the biological father of their adopted baby daughter will stop at nothing to get her back.
2012.  Stars: Sean Astin, Samaire Armstrong, Monet Mazur

*Abducted (Layover)*  - When the heiress of a luxury hotel chain is kidnapped at her rat trap motel outside Detroit by a band of ruthless human traffickers because she has seen too much, her oppressed assistant must figure out a way to rescue her.
2012. Stars: Lauren Holly, Kaylee DeFer, Joe Lando
